This is a simple project created Using Java programming language.
I used Eclipse IDE and Java 8. This project containing the following programs:

               1. Calculating Area of a circle.
               2. Calculating Area of a Rectangle.
               3. Calculating Perimeter of a circle.
               4. Calculating Perimeter of a Rectangle.
               5. Differentiating Odd and Even numbers.
               6. Finding the largest and smallest number in an Array.
               
Note: You can download this project and import it in eclipse to test the code.

                        ----- Happy Coding -----